{"tid":1159213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"響應中聯辦號召　建制派周六起擺街站撐修例","createTime":"2019-05-17T13:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T23:24:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b291dba7ab09979de6ea2e8abed022ce0b716dbf","tid":1159213,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/d8Sp3gMGjvK2nRpMZoIwDw--~B/aD00MDA7dz01MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190416a201529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fd8Sp3gMGjvK2nRpMZoIwDw--~B%2FaD00MDA7dz01MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190416a201529.jpg&h=a6730b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦主任王志民今午（17日）召集港區人大代表及一眾政協到中聯辦，宣告中央支持港府修訂《逃犯條例》後，建制派迅即以行動回應，參與會面的黃英豪以保公義撐修例大聯盟召集人身分發出採訪通知，表示修訂已經進入立法會審議階段，大聯盟將由5月18日（周六）下午開始，在港島、九龍和新界的主要地區擺設街站，稱要讓廣大市民對條例修訂有更多的了解，並發動更多市民加入網上聯署支持行動。大聯盟今午於中環舉行啟動儀式，預料會設40個街站。<br />\n<br />\n建制派團體對上一次推出大型街站行動，要數到2014年反佔中、 支持政改。有建制派指出，今次中聯辦號召建制派大搞文宣及行動支持港府，行動模式也類近2014年。"},{"pid":"80998e734503c28298e81450de4fc5f8a430562e","tid":1159213,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:41:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190517/s00001/1558098667776/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190517%2Fs00001%2F1558098667776%2F&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=df765aaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190517%2Fs00001%2F1558098667776%2F&h=a6fb92df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190517/s00001/1558098667776/</a>"},{"pid":"3ed98fd7db3269fb98074edaaa07e4aa88629004","tid":1159213,"uid":242917,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"r